snippet.title: Where Angels Meet: A Cinematic VR Experience - AVAILABLE NOW for Oculus Rift
snippet.description:
Have you ever wondered what it would be like to be an angel? Where Angels Meet is an extraordinary virtual reality experience coming exclusively to the Oculus Rift. This experience will give viewers a unique look into the life of a young man named Marcus, while journeying through beautiful landscapes and incredible environments.

Now Available - https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1741878345881014/

For more info - www.whereangelsmeet.com
